channel.title: No-one can connect to my Server
channel.description:
OK, Before you flame me about their being the EXACT same post down below.. It's not the same problem.
Okay, my problem; People CAN connect to my LD server but NOT my HD server, this leads me to beleive it's not portforward problem.
Can anyone clarify what files I would need and what files they would need.
Anyone help would be welcomed! Thanks.
